{"tid":1329222,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 日本「京都動畫」公司工作室被縱火　據報增至10死近40人傷","createTime":"2019-07-18T06:50:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T13:22:42.000Z","uid":60545,"like":1,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"9371956c24571f107df000396f5eea4037c6178c","tid":1329222,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T06:50:13.000Z","msg":"日本「京都動畫公司」位於京都伏見區的工作室，懷疑被人縱火，共同社引述警方表示，增至最少10人死亡，近40人受傷。警方拘捕一名41歲男子，懷疑他在現場淋潑汽油。<br />\n<br />\n事發在當地早上大約十時半，有目擊者說，工作室傳出爆炸聲，之後見到二樓及三樓有火光冒出，濃煙升上半空。亦有目擊者表示，疑犯當時一邊點火，一邊大叫。當局派出30架消防車及救護車到場救援，疑犯同樣受傷送院。 <br />\n<br />\n京都動畫公司在1981年成立，擁有大約160名員工，公司曾經製作多部著名動畫，包括《涼宮春日的憂鬱》、《K-ON！輕音少女》等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1469024-20190718.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1469024-20190718.htm&d=MciEVzKn1v3nDYmPhzNAyluXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=bf10b402\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1469024-20190718.htm&h=759924df\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1469024-20190718.htm</a>"},{"pid":"82ee4d58a4ef9ed4f896290abd53db4876757e0e","tid":1329222,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T06:52:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1976278f1b2f65d0297642b7f1b1613572eb8fc","tid":1329222,"uid":1255,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T06:53:05.000Z","msg":"留名睇 毒撚真係好恐怖"},{"pid":"2990692d536624bf1d39c105e71a7b94000b5337","tid":1329222,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b1976278f1b2f65d0297642b7f1b1613572eb8fc","tid":1329222,"uid":1255,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T06:53:05.000Z","msg":"留名睇 毒撚真係好恐怖"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T06:54:25.000Z","msg":"燒咗人間公司咪以後冇得睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji